{"id":"api/common/http/provideHttpClient","title":"provideHttpClient","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/http\", \"name\": \"@angular/common/http\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/http/provideHttpClient\", \"name\": \"provideHttpClient\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common/http\">@angular/common/http</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/http/src/provider.ts#L77-L144\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"providehttpclient\">provideHttpClient<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient#providehttpclient\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2r2pz53g5nb874f924bo41ij0\">将 Angular 的 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClient</a></code> 服务配置为可注入。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a></span>(...features: <a href=\"api/common/http/HttpFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpFeature</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/common/http/HttpFeatureKind\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpFeatureKind</a>&gt;[]): <a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"38fwf35xy1ajri4niursk05yy\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>features</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpFeature</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/common/http/HttpFeatureKind\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpFeatureKind</a>&gt;[]</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withInterceptors\"><code>withInterceptors</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withInterceptorsFromDi\"><code>withInterceptorsFromDi</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withXsrfConfiguration\"><code>withXsrfConfiguration</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withNoXsrfProtection\"><code>withNoXsrfProtection</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withJsonpSupport\"><code>withJsonpSupport</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withRequestsMadeViaParent\"><code>withRequestsMadeViaParent</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/http/withFetch\"><code>withFetch</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aasi9fjgunqto1fb7gqi4r08i\">默认情况下，<code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClient</a></code> 将配置为注入，其默认选项是对传出请求的 XSRF 保护。可以通过将特性函数传递给 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a></code> 来提供其他配置选项。例如，可以用 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/withInterceptors\" class=\"code-anchor\">withInterceptors</a>(...)</code> 特性添加 HTTP 拦截器。</p>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ep666arkt8udyv7fi2drw9w7q\">强烈建议为使用服务器端渲染的应用启用\n<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API\"><code>fetch</code></a>以获得更好的性能和兼容性。要启用\n<code>fetch</code>，请将\n<code><a href=\"api/common/http/withFetch\" class=\"code-anchor\">withFetch</a>()</code>特性添加到应用程序根目录下的\n<code><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a>()</code>调用中。</p>\n<code-example>\n<a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a>(<a href=\"api/common/http/withFetch\" class=\"code-anchor\">withFetch</a>());\n</code-example>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/com